title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 3 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 3 2022
description:
Montage of Democrats supporting Defund the Police movement that Dems would rather you don't hear. Blood of the current crime wave is on these Democrats' hands. Bill O'Reilly joins Clay and Buck to discuss his new book: Killing the Legends: The Lethal Danger of Celebrity and his outlook on the midterms and 2024 presidential race. Betting markets surging toward GOP winning House, 50-50 on Senate. C&B end the hour on calls about crime surges.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
